OL,3,CCooper speaks to Rubio as US threatens
OL,4,C'most intense day' of Iran war
OL,6,FThe Foreign Secretary has emphasised
OL,7,F"close co-ordination" on Middle
OL,8,FEastern security in a call with her US
OL,9,Fcounterpart as Washington threatened
OL,10,Fits "most intense day" of strikes on
OL,11,FIran.
OL,13,FYvette Cooper's conversation with US
OL,14,Fsecretary of state Marco Rubio on
OL,15,FTuesday evening came after American B1
OL,16,Fbombers were seen taking off from RAF
OL,17,FFairford in Gloucestershire and
OL,18,Fexplosions were reported in Tehran.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]rD@EOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
