OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773194862
OL,3,CCooper speaks to Rubio as US threatens
OL,4,C'most intense day' of Iran war
OL,6,FA spokesman for Mr Rubio said the pair
OL,7,Fhad "underscored the importance of
OL,8,Fcontinued close co-ordination on the
OL,9,Fsecurity of the broader Middle East".
OL,11,FWhile the UK has not struck Iran
OL,12,Fdirectly, Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,13,Fpreviously granted an American request
OL,14,Fto use RAF Fairford and the British
OL,15,Fbase on Diego Garcia to strike Iranian
OL,16,Fmissile sites threatening other
OL,17,Fcountries in the region.
OL,26,@oD@EOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
