OL,3,CCooper speaks to Rubio as US threatens
OL,4,C'most intense day' of Iran war
OL,6,FEarlier on Tuesday, US defence
OL,7,Fsecretary Pete Hegseth said the day
OL,8,Fwould bring "our most intense day of
OL,9,Fstrikes inside Iran: the most
OL,10,Ffighters, the most bombers, the most
OL,11,Fstrikes".
OL,13,FHe also said the previous 24 hours had
OL,14,Fseen Iran fire the lowest amount of
OL,15,Fmissiles it had launched since the
OL,16,Fcrisis began.
OL,18,FIranian strikes continued to hit the
OL,19,Fcountry's neighbours on Tuesday,
OL,20,Fincluding Bahrain and the UAE.
OL,26,@pD@MOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
