OL,3,CCooper speaks to Rubio as US threatens
OL,4,C'most intense day' of Iran war
OL,6,FUK forces continue to engage in
OL,7,Fdefensive operations in the region,
OL,8,Fwith the Royal Navy destroyer HMS
OL,9,FDragon currently en route to the
OL,10,Feastern Mediterranean to assist in
OL,11,Fprotecting Cyprus.
OL,13,FThe ship, which left Portsmouth a week
OL,14,Fafter its deployment was announced, is
OL,15,Fcapable of shooting down drones and
OL,16,Fballistic missiles fired by Iran and
OL,17,Fits proxies as the Middle East crisis
OL,18,Fcontinues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773194862
OL,3,CCooper speaks to Rubio as US threatens
OL,4,C'most intense day' of Iran war
OL,6,FThe Government has also announced it
OL,7,Fis preparing a second vessel, the
OL,8,Flanding ship RFA Lyme Bay, for
OL,9,Fpotential deployment if the crisis
OL,10,Fdeepens.
OL,12,FDomestic concern remained focused on
OL,13,Fthe impact of the cost of living, as
OL,14,Fthe conflict continued to restrict
OL,15,Fshipping through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,16,F` a vital route for oil and gas
OL,17,Fsupplies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
