OL,3,CCooper speaks to Rubio as US threatens
OL,4,C'most intense day' of Iran war
OL,6,FMarkets calmed after US President
OL,7,FDonald Trump suggested the military
OL,8,Faction would be a "short-term
OL,9,Fexcursion" rather than a more
OL,10,Fprolonged war and threatened "death,
OL,11,Ffire and fury" against Iran unless
OL,12,Fvessels were allowed through the
OL,13,Fstrait.
OL,15,FBut nervousness around the potential
OL,16,Fimpact of higher energy costs still
OL,17,Flingered.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@JO]rD@^OUsD@NO]
