PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773194862
OL,3,CCooper speaks to Rubio as US threatens
OL,4,C'most intense day' of Iran war
OL,6,FA spokesman for the organisers told
OL,7,Fthe BBC's The World Tonight that it
OL,8,Fwas "a sad day for freedom of
OL,9,Fexpression", adding: "This
OL,10,Fdemonstration has taken place for the
OL,11,Flast 40 years peacefully."
OL,13,FMPs from both Labour and the
OL,14,FConservatives had called for the march
OL,15,Fto be banned over claims it includes
OL,16,Fsupport for the Tehran regime and
OL,17,Fantisemitism.
OL,26,@pD@EOUqD@KO]qD@VOUsD@ZO]
